&lt;li&gt;Develop backend services and APIs that integrate with vehicle systems, cloud infrastructure, and external partner platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build tools that enable fleet monitoring, vehicle health tracking, maintenance workflows, and operational decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
