&lt;li&gt;Own features end-to-end: scoping, implementation, testing, deployment, and iteration based on user feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to frontend architecture decisions, component libraries, and shared platform patterns used across the org.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve system reliability through testing, monitoring, alerting, and production support practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
