&lt;li&gt;Support Safety and Ops teams during road-collision calls and other safety-related escalations, ensuring timely documentation, communication, and next steps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide frontline supervisors and leads with guidance on documentation, coaching conversations, and navigating routine HR matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with key HR processes for a large, hourly workforce, including onboarding touchpoints, workplace support needs, and shift-based communication updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spot patterns across teams and shifts to surface early signals related to safety, performance, or engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
