&lt;p&gt;The mandate of the prediction team is to use advanced machine learning techniques to improve the behavior of the Nuro Driver.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a key member of the Prediction and Smart Agents team, you will focus on building state-of-the-art models for predicting the behavior of surrounding traffic. These models are crucial for our autonomous system, as they will be deployed onboard as part of our planning stack and used offboard for realistic closed-loop simulation.&lt;/p&gt;
